included.description: Sunmool is building a web platform to allow people to exchange or give away their unused outfits with the goal of using technology to enable the kind of gift economy that preceded society's use of money.  Earth is currently at a tipping point in its history as human activity has increasingly brought the planet out of balance. Key to this problem is our current economic system which encourages material consumption and compels consumers to continually buy new products.
